Data Cleanup:

Project Towers

Towers: decided by creating three columns, the sum, and max of “Number of Towers Column, and also extracting the max number from tower description. When two or all three of these agreed, that was the number. After that, I took the largest number of the three that was between 0 and 100. If both of these failed, the value was removed. This created 152 NAs out of 1222

Units: added up all units from each stage of the project

Value: added up all units from each stage of the project

Area: added up all units from each stage of the project

Floors: added up all units from each stage of the project

Completion date was filtered by year, eliminating 3 projects pre 2007
